<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Razina 6 – Prijava</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: sans-serif; padding: 40px; max-width: 800px; margin: auto; text-align: center;">
  <h1>🔐 Razina 6: Prijavi se</h1>

  <form method="POST" style="margin-top: 30px;">
    <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email" required
           style="padding: 10px; font-size: 16px; width: 250px; margin-bottom: 10px;" /><br />
    <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Lozinka" required
           style="padding: 10px; font-size: 16px; width: 250px;" /><br />
    <button type="submit" style="padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 10px;">Prijavi se</button>
  </form>

  <% if (flag) { %>
    <p style="margin-top: 30px;"><strong>Flag:</strong> <%= flag %></p>

    <form method="POST" style="margin-top: 20px;">
      <input type="text" name="flagInput" placeholder="Unesi flag za nastavak" required
             style="padding: 10px; font-size: 16px; width: 250px;" />
      <button type="submit" style="padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 16px;">Pošalji flag</button>
    </form>
  <% } %>

  <% if (error) { %>
    <p style="color: red; margin-top: 20px;"><%= error %></p>
  <% } %>

  <hr style="margin: 40px auto; width: 60%;" />

  <img src="https://media4.giphy.com/media/v1.Y2lkPTc5MGI3NjExbHR0eGUwbG84eWx5ZWlheXhpajliZml3aHR0M2h5a3RqZ3Y1ZmwxZCZlcD12MV9pbnRlcm5hbF9naWZfYnlfaWQmY3Q9Zw/l4485XkNjWw4locDki/giphy.gif"
       alt="Login hint" style="max-width: 100%; border-radius: 8px;" />

  <p style="margin-top: 10px; color: gray;">
    💡 Hint: Ponekad ne moraš biti ono što ti sustav kaže da jesi.
    <br />Ali moraš znati kako se prikazati kao ono što trebaš biti.
  </p>

  <!-- Skriveni hint -->
  <footer id="footer" style="margin-top: 50px; color: #999;"
          data-hint="Kada presretnes zahtjev, u njega dodaj &role=admin.">
    © INCTF 2025 – Promjena počinje iznutra.
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
